{"tid":596723,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Android電話大量中毒,支那牌子成重災區","createTime":"2018-03-18T03:02:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T06:31:51.000Z","uid":48234,"like":51,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"f012ad529a604b358452583d5660ea19df47b2b4","tid":596723,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:02:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i1.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/android_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi1.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2Fandroid_2.jpg&h=abe8cf22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n防毒軟件公司CHECK POINT近日發現，多款支那電話中毒，不斷受到惡意廣告騷擾，受影響最嚴重的手機均屬支那牌子，包括榮耀、華為、小米、OPPO和VIVO等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i0.wp.com/hkjam.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/03/5aab687eae19a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fhkjam.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F03%2F5aab687eae19a.jpg&h=e97c0c69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最詭異的是，該惡意程式並非因為用戶下載有毒程式或瀏覽某些惡意網站而中招，CHECK POINT認為極有可能用戶在購買電話時，電話已經藏有病毒。<br />\n<br />\n而在用戶買電話時已中毒的原因，CHECK POINT估計可能是某些分銷商在批發過程中植入惡意軟件，亦有可能是支那植入監察軟件到電話中時出錯。<br />\n<br />\nCHECK POINT建議，最佳的保障自己方法是不要用支那牌子電話。<br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkjam.com/?p=10292\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkjam.com%2F%3Fp%3D10292&d=XioBUHAkMQFiHr5iJCa0c6WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=5afa4c45\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkjam.com/?p=10292</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n五毛狗,今次點撚解駁呀</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab0f79e7318eb7cbdea7426a3ec5a6c13b819be8","tid":596723,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">更正:<br />\n五毛狗,今次點撚解駁呀?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18dd144338de16a605c74c7386d5a6d0ebc2168f","tid":596723,"uid":48234,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ab0f79e7318eb7cbdea7426a3ec5a6c13b819be8","tid":596723,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:03:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">更正:<br />\n五毛狗,今次點撚解駁呀?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:04:14.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">又打錯,屌<br />\n五毛狗,今次點撚樣駁呀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"946cd0584d3baa5b8cd65dc5e9f6b69efb9a514a","tid":596723,"uid":1085,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:07:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d5893e3bfb56927592baaccf3456e3e479660fa4","tid":596723,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"946cd0584d3baa5b8cd65dc5e9f6b69efb9a514a","tid":596723,"uid":1085,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:07:08.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:08:57.000Z","msg":"呢句夠好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9739a78ddfd0b2c6f69faf0655b75a272a95a786","tid":596723,"uid":164092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T03:14:08.000Z","msg":"Oneplu